All of the TRASHY TRASH DJs are clocking in at over 15 years of DJing experience, opening for artists such as Modeselektor, Dj Craze, Dj Jazzy Jeff, Talib Kweli, Glass Candy, DJ KRUSH, Juan Maclean, DJ Qbert, Amon Tobin, Grandmaster Flash, Daedelus, Dead Prez, James Pants, Guilty Simpson, Shlohmo, Joker, Nosaj Thing, The Martin Bros, Bonobo, Prefuse73, Morgan Geist, Boys Noize, Lusine, Michna, Onra, Take, Slugabed, OM Unit, Truckasauras, Egyptian Lover and many more.

Their most recent endeavors include a collaboration with SNAP! 90s Dance Party crew out of Portland, Oregon... In Seattle you can catch them Deejaying at "Stop Biting" (Tuesdays at LOFI), "Midnight Hotline Rendezvous" last Fridays at LOFI & Mondays "Industry Standard" at The Hideout w/ Introcut. In Portland you can check out Nathan Detroit, Freaky Outty, Colin Jones & Maxx Bass rockin parties like "Booty Basement" at spots like, Holocene, Tube, Valentines, Dig A Pony, Yes & No, Saucebox, Groove Suite, The Branx, Rotture & more!

In the meantime, we'll be looking for the perfect beat. Much thanks to all the artists, dj's, dancers, promoters, mcs, drunks, beer sluts, bartenders, punks, degenerates, mommies, pappies and babies that we are so fortunate to call our friends and family!!!
